---
title: Butternut Squash Risotto with Sage and Garlic
description: Warming, delicious and simple enough to rustle up in 35 minutes, this seasonal vegetarian risotto is Italian comfort food on tip-top form. Crispy butternut squash roasted with sage, is a simple flavour combination which takes the taste of this dish to the next level, and is one you’ll be dreaming about for days to follow. Top with cheese for an irresistibly creamy finish and tuck in!
